A '''constructor''' device was a [[Gree (species)/Legends|Gree]] machine used to construct [[hypergate]]s. Constructors were operated exclusively by [[Master (Gree)|Gree Masters]]. Constructors could assemble almost any sort of equipment using basic materials and an example of the item that was to be created.<ref name="The Gree Enclave">{{JournalCite|8|The Gree Enclave}}</ref>

